title=Vikings Fill Initial 2019 Practice Squad|url=https://www.vikings.com/news/vikings-practice-squad-2019|website=Vikings.com|date=September 1, 2019}}</ref> He was promoted to the active roster on October 12, 2019.<ref>{{cite web|title=Vikings Sign Cameron Smith to Active Roster, Waive Davion Davis|url=https://www.vikings.com/news/vikings-sign-cameron-smith-to-active-roster-waive-davion-davis|author=Peters, Craig|website=Vikings.com|date=October 12, 2019}}</ref> He was waived again on November 2, 2019 and re-signed to the practice squad.<ref>{{cite web|title=Vikings Add Holton Hill To 53-Man Roster, Waive Cam Smith|url=https://www.vikings.com/news/vikings-add-holton-hill-to-53-man-roster-waive-cam-smith|website=Vikings.com|date=November 2, 2019|accessdate=November 3, 2019}}</ref> He was promoted back to the active roster on November 26, 2019.<ref>{{cite web|title=Vikings Sign Cameron Smith to Active Roster|url=https://www.vikings.com/news/vikings-sign-cameron-smith-to-active-roster|website=Vikings.com|date=November 26, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.usctrojans.com/sports/m-footbl/mtt/cameron_smith_953935.html USC Trojans bio]\n\n{{Pac-12 Player of the Year}}\n{{Vikings2019DraftPicks}}\n{{Minnesota Vikings roster navbox}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Smith, Cameron}}\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American football linebackers]]\n[[Category:People from Granite Bay, California]]\n[[Category:Players of American football from California]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Roseville, California]]\n[[Category:USC Trojans football players]]\n[[Category:Minnesota Vikings players]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use American English|date = September 2019}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date = September 2019}}\n{{short description|American football inside linebacker}}\n{{Infobox NFL biography\n| name         = Cameron Smith\n| image        = \n| image_size   = \n| alt          = \n| caption      = \n| current_team = Minnesota Viki