as the seven best Inside Linebacker in his class and 190th best player overall.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://247sports.com/player/cameron-smith-32275/|title=Cameron Smith, Minnesota Vikings, Inside Linebacker|website=[[247Sports.com]]|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]|language=en-US|access-date=September 2, 2019}}</ref> He committed to the [[University of Southern California]] (USC) to play college football where he joined the Beta-Sigma chapter of [[Tau Kappa Epsilon]] fraternity.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://reignoftroy.com/2014/05/21/usc-football-recruiting-cameron-smith-commitment-announcement/|title=Cameron Smith Commits to USC|last=Shaw|first=Hank|date=May 21, 2014|website=[[FanSided]]|language=en-US|access-date=September 2, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==College career==\n===Statistics===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Year !! rowspan=\"2\"|Team !! rowspan=\"2\"|{{tooltip|G|Games played}} !! rowspan=\"2\"|{{tooltip|GS|Games started}} !! colspan=\"7\" |Tackles\n|-\n! {{tooltip|Solo|Solo Tackles}} !! {{tooltip|Ast| Assisted Tackles}} !! {{tooltip|Total|Total Tackles}} !! {{tooltip|Loss|Tackles for Loss}} !! {{tooltip|Yds|Tackle for Loss yards}} !! {{tooltip|Sack|Quarterback Sacks}} !! {{tooltip|Yds|Sacks yards}}\n|-\n| [[2015 NCAA Division I FBS football season|2015]] || [[2015 USC Trojans football team|USC]] || 10 || 9 || 45 || 33 || 78 || 1.0 || 9 || 1.0 || 9\n|-\n| [[2016 NCAA Division I FBS football season|2016]] || [[2016 USC Trojans football team|USC]] || 12 || 12 || 43 || 36 || 79 || 7.0 || 24 || 1.0 || 6\n|- class=\"sortbottom\" style=\"background:#eee;\"\n| colspan=2 | '''Career''' || 22 || 21 || 88 || 69 || 157 || 8.0 || 33 || 2.0 || 15\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Year !! rowspan=\"2\"|Team !! colspan=\"6\" |Interceptions / Coverage !! colspan=\"4\" |Fumbles\n|-\n! {{tooltip|INT| Interceptions}} !! {{tooltip|Yds|Interception yards}} !! {{tooltip|Avg|Avg yard interception